data.description: This one-of-a-kind home features 6 large bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The property is situated on almost 2 acres of land, surrounded by cornfields on 2 sides, providing a peaceful country ambiance. The home boasts a formal living room and dining room, sunroom, family room with fireplace, and a huge bonus room, perfect for relaxing and entertaining guests. One of the bedrooms has access to outside which would make a perfect office or in-laws quarters.  The kitchen is equipped with double wall ovens, a dishwasher, smooth top range, and ample cabinets. The property has more than enough parking, with a 2-car garage and a 2-car carport, as well as additional spaces for guests. The fenced-in backyard is a true oasis, featuring a large wood deck and basketball court, ideal for outdoor entertainment. Mini barn is also a plus for extra storage. Despite the country feel, the property is conveniently located, with Johnson Memorial hospital less than a mile away and beautiful downtown Franklin just minutes away, offering plenty of shopping and dining options. Franklin College is also conveniently nearby. NOTE; lot size is not listed correctly, see agent remarks.
